            <div class="article_col-main article_col-main-left article_main">
              <div class="article-body" itemprop="articleBody">
                    <p> MEET THE PRESS - MARCH 13, 2016 </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> CHUCK TODD: </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> This Sunday, fear, loathing, and now violence on the Trump campaign trail. Days before make or break primaries on &quot;Separation Tuesday,&quot; Trump's opponents blame him. </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> SEN. TED CRUZ: </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> When you have a campaign that affirmatively encourages violence. </p>
                
              
                    <div class="ad-container ad-container_default ad-container_mobile ad-hide">
                      <div class="ad-label ad-hide">
                      	<a href="http://www.nbcnews.com/id/31066137/media-kit/" target="_blank">advertisement</a>
                      </div>
                      <div class="ad-content ad-xs box1" data-placement="box1"></div>
                    </div>
              
              
                    <p> CHUCK TODD: </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> And openly worry what will happen if he's the nominee. </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> SEN. MARCO RUBIO: </p>
                
              
              
              
